cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1-U port to an out-of-range value of 99999 will cause GTP-U tunnel establishment failures and prevent user plane data transmission.

du.explanation_en: Setting the zero correlation zone configuration to an invalid value of 999 will cause PRACH detection errors and prevent UE random access.
du.explanation_zh: 將零相關區配置設定為無效值 999 會導致 PRACH 檢測錯誤，並阻止 UE 隨機接入。
